WEBVTT

00:00:01.490 --> 00:00:07.490
For thousands of years, people have wondered how life came to be.

00:00:07.490 --> 00:00:16.789
Knowing how we came to be here could be an important step toward knowing why we are here.

00:00:16.789 --> 00:00:25.789
Although science can explain many things, some people feel that it's not able to provide satisfying answers to the really important questions.

00:00:25.789 --> 00:00:28.789
Questions such as, is there a purpose in life?

00:00:28.789 --> 00:00:38.020
They also believe that the natural world gives compelling evidence that life was created.

00:00:38.020 --> 00:00:53.740
Could that evidence help you find a purpose in life?

00:00:53.740 --> 00:00:57.740
Why not investigate for yourself and reach your own conclusion?

00:00:57.740 --> 00:01:04.890
To learn more, read the brochure was Life Created.

00:01:04.890 --> 00:01:12.890
You can download it free of charge from JW.org or you can obtain a copy from any of Jehovah's Witnesses.
